function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	followerYorin = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Scos_Yorin_Follower")

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerYorin) then
		--Yorin moves to the Weeping Cairns entrance
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(followerYorin, false)
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerYorin)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CON_CALL_WEEPINGCAIRNS, followerYorin)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerYorin, LOC_YORIN_WC, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerYorin, LOC_YORIN_WC)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(followerYorin, CON_CALL_WEEPINGCAIRNS)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerYorin)
	Hydra.EventSend("WCArrive")

end
